Class BaseDynamicExtensionsException

java.lang.Object
  java.lang.Throwable
      java.lang.Exception
          edu.common.dynamicextensions.exception.BaseDynamicExtensionsException
All Implemented Interfaces:
DynamicExtensionExceptionInterface, java.io.Serializable
Direct Known Subclasses:
DynamicExtensionsApplicationException, DynamicExtensionsSystemException
public abstract class BaseDynamicExtensionsException
extends java.lang.Exception
implements DynamicExtensionExceptionInterface

This class acts as a base exception from which all the exceptions will extend. The class holds the information about the cause of the exception along with the unique error code.

Author:
Vishvesh Mulay
